How to run
Prepare the cleaned CSV (if you haven’t yet)

Run your existing data_processor.py to generate cleaned_dataset.csv.
Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

Use your PowerShell and run a one-time install:
Optional command:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Train the MLP

Run from the project root using module mode so relative imports work:
Optional command:
python -m model.train_mlp
Artifacts and metrics will be saved under saved_artifacts/model_vYYYYMMDD_HHMMSS/.
